landing.headline: Fullstack Software Engineer, Solutions Architect
landing.bio: Enthusiastic software engineer with more than 7 years of industry experience, contributing to both small and enterprise-level business applications built on mobile and web platforms. Familiar with current development trends, tools, and best practices, as well as SDLC methodologies and design patterns. Proficient with C#, Java, .NET, MS SQL, Angular, Flutter, React, Git, and Docker, and eager to learn new languages and emerging technologies.
